item.title: Dittenhafer Airways Status
item.description: As of 11:49pm, there are 312 FlyteNet enabled aircraft in flight. Of these, 92% are green, while 7% are yellow and 1% are red. N923JB has reported a new MPS related alert and N123CO from JFK to LAX has more users than usual.
